                <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #059669;">ğŸ“ File Upload: Ready</div>
                <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #059669;">ğŸ§  Knowledge Base: Loaded</div>
                <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #059669;">ğŸ¤– AI Agent: Ready</div>
                <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #059669;">ğŸ’¾ Memory: Operational</div>
                <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280;">â±ï¸ Init: {initialization_status.get('init_time', 'N/A')}</div>
